story, in international relations, and in comparative area studies, will have to take into account Frank's exciting reassessment of our global economic past and future.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCapitalismxHistory. 0aCompetition, InternationalxHistory. 0aEconomic history. 0aInternational economic relationsxHistory. 7aHISTORY / Asia / General.2bisacsh  aacademic.  aamerican colonies.  aasia.  aasian history.  acolonialism.  ademographics.  aeast asia.  aeastern world.  aeconomy.  aeurocentrism.  aglobal economy.  aglobal.  ahistoriography.  ahistory.  aindustrial world.  aindustrialization.  ainternational relations.  amarx.  amarxism.  aphilosophy.  ascholarly.  asocial history.  asocial theory.  atheorists.  aweber.  awestern world.  aworld economy.  aworld market.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000z978311063534840uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052092131340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520921313423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520921313/original  a978-3-11-063534-8  University of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles